<reg_short_dscr>:
Time tick configuration
------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
Counter value used to generate a tick every 16777216 ns used for ASM aging logic.
------------------------------
<field_enc>:
Set to the number of system clock cycles in 16777216 ns (flooring) - 1. For example if the system clock period is 6.4 ns set TIME_TICK_VAL to 16777216/6.4 - 1.
